Implementation complete. Here's what was built:

**`src/core/transcripts.ts`** — Core module with:
- `findTranscriptDir(worktreePath)` — Locates Claude Code transcript directories by encoding the worktree path
- `listSessions(dir)` — Lists all session JSONL files with metadata (start time, duration, event count)
- `parseTranscript(path)` — Parses JSONL transcripts and extracts tool_use, text, and thinking events
- `getToolIcon(toolName)` — Maps tool names to icons (`$` Bash, `r` Read, `w` Write, `e` Edit, `/` Grep, `*` Glob, `>>` Agent)
- `formatDuration(secs)` — Human-readable duration formatting

**`src/commands/logs.ts`** — Command with 4 modes:
- `hive logs [agent]` — Shows recent events from the latest session per agent
- `hive logs --list` — Lists all sessions per agent
- `hive logs --session <id>` — Full transcript for a specific session (prefix matching)
- `hive logs --follow` — Live-tails active transcript using chokidar
- All modes support `--json` output

**Supporting changes:**
- Registered in `src/index.ts`
- Shell completions added for bash, zsh, and fish in `src/commands/completion.ts`
- 25 tests in `tests/core/transcripts.test.ts`

